    <text>
        <body>
            <entry xml:id="entry_gec-færsæn" xml:lang="os-x-digor">
                <form type="lemma"><orth>gec-færsæn</orth></form>
                <usg><lang/></usg>
                <sense xml:id="sense_d3473e72"><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                        <q>гаданье на горохе</q>
                    </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                        <q>favomancy</q>
                    </abv:tr></sense>
                <etym xml:lang="ru">Ср. <mentioned xml:id="mentioned_d3473e84" xml:lang="kbd"><lang/>
                        <w>geš</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:id="mentioned_d3473e89" xml:lang="kbd-x-crc"><lang/>
                        <w>genš</w>
                        <gloss><q>горох</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:id="mentioned_d3473e97" xml:lang="kbd-x-crc"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>фасоль</q></gloss></mentioned>. Во второй части %ifærs(yn)%i
                    ‘спрашивать’, ‘гадать’ (см. <ref type="xr" target="#entry_færsyn"/>).</etym>
                <etym xml:lang="en">Compare <mentioned xml:id="mentioned_d3473e108" xml:lang="kbd"><lang/>
                        <w>geš</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:id="mentioned_d3473e113" xml:lang="kbd-x-crc"><lang/>
                        <w>genš</w>
                        <gloss><q>pea</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:id="mentioned_d3473e121" xml:lang="kbd-x-crc"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>haricot</q></gloss></mentioned>. In the second part there is
                    %ifærs(yn)%i ‘ask’, ‘tell fortunes’ (see <ref type="xr" target="#entry_færsyn"/>).</etym>
            </entry>
